        "_account_id": 112,
        "name": "Oleg Drokin",
        "email": "green@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "green"
      },
      "date": "2015-11-19 20:41:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nBruno, I just checked and it seems I was always hitting test 7 problems even before this patch.\n\nInteresting, I'll do some more analysis, I guess.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
